Package modules.idt

This package contains classes and interfaces needed to manage the IDT Administration module.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IdtDao DAO Interface for accessing IDT data from some external data source.
 

Class Summary
IDTFactory A factory for creating IDT Administration related objects.
IdtFrame The main window for the IDT administration module which allows the administrator to modiy IDT reticketing recrods
IdtIbatisDaoImpl This is the iBatis implementation of IdtDao interface for IDT Administration data store.
IdtModifyQtyInputDialog This is a dialog for entering the quantity sent value that is to be used to change the quantity of a SKU.
IdtSkuFilterInputDialog Dialog for inputing SKU filter data.
